In VM configuration, choose Bridged Adaptor
		     use 20GB disk

Choose Gnome Desktop + Development tools
Add saluser account during install

From VM menu Install Guest Additions from cd image


In Settings enable the Network interface
su
yum install xterm
            xorg-x11-fonts-misc
            java-1.7.0-openjdk-devel
            boost-python
            boost-python-devel
            maven
            swig

systemctl stop iptables
systemctl stop firewalld

systemctl enable iptables
add rules to /etc/sysconfig/iptables
systemctl start iptables

Make sure network is up and working.

